---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import DonateButton from '../components/shared/DonateButton.astro';
import QuoteBanner from '../components/shared/QuoteBanner.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Access"
  description="Bringing Montessori adolescent programming to communities that have never had access — equity is not a value statement, it's our core mission."
  heroTitle="Montessori for Everyone"
  heroSubtitle=""
>
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <section class="page-section">
      <p>
        "The more I learned about the Montessori pedagogy, the more I wished it were available to all communities. Every child should grow up in these interconnected environments that foster healthy independence and perseverance, which in turn nurtures a strong sense of self-assurance and care for the world around them.
      </p>
      <p>
        Montessori diploma teacher-training courses can cost upward of $14,000, and the majority of Montessori programs worldwide are private institutions with high tuition rates. This has always disheartened me. I have worked for a few private schools, and my heart always carried a quiet whisper: <em>'I have to help make this wisdom accessible to more communities, regardless of income.'</em>
      </p>
      <p>
        This is where the philanthropy component of <strong>Montessori for Adolescents</strong> was born. I truly believe that this is education for a more peaceful world — empowering young people to become their most authentic selves rooted in integrity and an interdependent worldview."
      </p>
      <p class="signature">Jarin, Founder of Montessori for Adolescents</p>
    </section>

    <section class="page-section">
      <h2>How Your Support Helps</h2>
      <div class="impact-grid">
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>Training</h3>
          <p>Funding Montessori adolescent training for educators in communities where the cost would otherwise be a barrier.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>Programs</h3>
          <p>Helping communities create their own spaces for adolescents to learn, work, and grow together.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>On-Site Support</h3>
          <p>Being there in person — side by side — to help turn a vision into something real.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="page-section">
      <h2>Roadmap</h2>
      <div class="phases-grid">
        <div class="phase-card">
          <span class="phase-label">Phase 1</span>
          <h3>Foundation</h3>
          <span class="phase-goal">$5,000</span>
          <p>Cover core operations, registration and fees, maintain website, initial content and marketing.</p>
          <p class="phase-outcome"><strong>Outcome:</strong> The project becomes self-sustaining.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="phase-card">
          <span class="phase-label">Phase 2</span>
          <h3>Access Expansion</h3>
          <span class="phase-goal">$10,000</span>
          <p>Identify an under-served community (Bali or Kathmandu), assess need, provide resources, and research costs and local requirements.</p>
          <p class="phase-outcome"><strong>Outcome:</strong> A community is selected and groundwork begins.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="phase-card">
          <span class="phase-label">Phase 3</span>
          <h3>Direct Community Support</h3>
          <span class="phase-goal">$15,000</span>
          <p>Partner with local organizations, fund programming and licensing, source a Center for Study and Work location, and train and pay local teachers.</p>
          <p class="phase-outcome"><strong>Outcome:</strong> Launch a pilot program.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="phase-card">
          <span class="phase-label">Phase 4</span>
          <h3>Scale Impact</h3>
          <p>Expand to multiple communities, hire a program coordinator, and develop long-term sustainability.</p>
          <p class="phase-outcome"><strong>Outcome:</strong> Montessori adolescent programming reaches more communities around the world.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="page-section">
      <h2>Progress</h2>
      <div class="progress-tracker">
        <div class="progress-bar">
          <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 2.65%;"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-milestones">
          <div class="milestone" style="left: 5%;">
            <span class="milestone-amount">$1k</span>
            <span class="milestone-label">Registration</span>
          </div>
          <div class="milestone" style="left: 25%;">
            <span class="milestone-amount">$5k</span>
            <span class="milestone-label">Foundation</span>
          </div>
          <div class="milestone" style="left: 50%;">
            <span class="milestone-amount">$10k</span>
            <span class="milestone-label">Access</span>
          </div>
          <div class="milestone" style="left: 90%;">
            <span class="milestone-amount">$15k+</span>
            <span class="milestone-label">Pilot</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="progress-message">
          <strong>$530 raised</strong> — Montessori for Adolescents is not yet a 501(c)(3) but plans to register as soon as enough funds are raised to cover all registration and licensing fees. An average of $1,000 is needed for proper set-up.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="page-section text-center">
      <div class="donate-action">
        <DonateButton label="Support Our Work" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="page-section text-center">
      <h2>With Gratitude</h2>
      <p>This work is made possible by the generosity of people who believe in it.</p>
      <div class="donor-row">
        <span class="donor-chip">Shaukat Wadiwalla</span>
        <span class="donor-chip">Deborah Wadiwalla</span>
        <span class="donor-chip">Antony Chiang</span>
        <span class="donor-chip">William Lovett</span>
      </div>
      <div class="donor-row">
        <span class="donor-chip">Wagas Kurjee</span>
        <span class="donor-chip">Dr. Daniel Vo</span>
      </div>
      <div class="donor-row">
        <span class="donor-chip">Pavla Guggenheim</span>
        <span class="donor-chip">Ayan Goswami</span>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <QuoteBanner
    text="Education is the most powerful weapon which you can use to change the world."
    author="Nelson Mandela"
  />
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .page-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .page-section h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    color: var(--color-earth);
  }

  .page-section p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .impact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .impact-card {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .impact-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-terracotta);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .impact-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .signature {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-earth);
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .donate-action {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  /* Phases */
  .phases-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .phase-card {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .phase-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wider);
    color: var(--color-terracotta);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .phase-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-earth);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .phase-goal {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-terracotta);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .phase-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .phase-outcome {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Progress Tracker */
  .progress-tracker {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .progress-bar {
    height: 12px;
    background-color: var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background-color: var(--color-terracotta);
    border-radius: 6px;
    min-width: 4px;
    transition: width var(--transition-slow);
  }

  .progress-milestones {
    position: relative;
    height: 3rem;
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .milestone {
    position: absolute;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .milestone-amount {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-earth);
  }

  .milestone-label {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .progress-message {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
  }

  /* Donor Recognition */
  .donor-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .donor-row:first-of-type {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .donor-chip {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-lg);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-earth);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .impact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .phases-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .milestone-label {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
